Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look just like you did when you left me? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, give me an answer! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{op} 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{tlnote boyunoha talks all crass and shit} 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruder in the Alicia Room! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruder in the Alicia Room! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one target! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Block off the halls! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move a muscle! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here, Sir Izumo! Please, leave at once! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you leave. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait outside until I say otherwise. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, sir. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy with wings. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not expect us to meet again so soon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is my mom... what is this woman doing here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of the curse of Eve laid upon Altair? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of Eve? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be safe for a bit longer now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My throat's still feels a little strange. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the guys are okay? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fine. I made them promise not to be stupid. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They promised... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I want a promise from you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay! Nothing wrong here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the sky is covered up on this planet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe everyone on the planet longs for the sky, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why they fantasize about the Skies of Aquaria. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Jin... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, we were almost toast!{boyunoha starts here} 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not safe here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great time for Shrade to be taking a walk. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? What a freaking flake. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last I know the melody this world dances to. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an ugly sky. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life of this land is waning away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, how strange. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land and I are much alike. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaiting a death not far off. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I understand you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your power flowing, 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can see the nexus of that power. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out, assholes! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep me here! I said, let me out! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying? I should thank them for bringing me here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Mix. I'm gonna find you... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find him. I have to find High Commander Fudo... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've come this far. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really stands out, so it wasn't hard to track him here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can do to help. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done running away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:07:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find High Commander Fudo and take him back to the academy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shush? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Commander Fudo! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly took your time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I've been looking as hard as I could! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to look? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been with you the entire time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the market, on the trolley, and all through this town. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not move for but an instant. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my body journeys across Creation, I move not. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my soul lives throughout Eternity, I change not. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change not? Move not? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're "Fudo"... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. Fudo, Achala, the Immovable.{不動 = unmoving see also http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acalanatha} 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the meaning of the name, Fudo ZEN! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Commander Fudo, do you mean you've been alive for 12,000 years? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite. You should say 24,000 years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono Suzushiro, do you wish to know the whole truth? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it. I swore to myself I wouldn't run away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it would be to take. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will do. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can be truly cruel. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fourteen years ago, all of the Igura, the women of Altair, died out. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Jin! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin Muso was the last child born on Altair. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now? A planet without Iguras is doomed to a slow death. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you've been abducting women from our planet? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we want is a mother, to bear Altair's future. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that gives you the right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear the whole story, boy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is more to the truth you need to hear. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the rest is only more cruel. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Mix! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me! Where's Mix? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with gigantic big bangs! Your boss brought her a while ago! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl? Oh, you mean... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even move! {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the next hole's going to be bigger, and... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'll tell you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll let you off easy this time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, my power just doesn't work on living things, but still! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prisoner has escaped! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find you and hold you in my arms, Mix! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{cm} 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going now?{I couldn't wait to tl this segment because it's awesome} 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono Suzushiro. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see this donut, what do you think? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think it looks tasty? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold this donut still in my hand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, it is crossing the waters as quickly as this boat. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You find nothing wondrous about a donut crossing the sea? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the donut has vanished. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the secret: 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paradoxically, it is so close to you that you cannot see it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's in your stomach, High Commander. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The donut will be decomposed into its molecules, yet it will not truly disappear. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be incorporated into my body, and from a certain point of view, become Immovable. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking in Zen koans. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean by the "whole truth"? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is an entity that has been "immovably" sustaining this world for 12,000 years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immovably? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion of myth. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lies sleeping at the end of this journey.{our journey? his journey? her journey?} 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pointless! I'm digging blind here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruder sighted in block X33! Get him! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Stay away from me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you. Keep out of my way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo's in the Alicia Room! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with the Vegan intruder! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of Eve did not end with the extinction of Iguras on Altair. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also affected the Iguras we took from your planet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at last we found Iguras powerful enough to resist the curse. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare Iguras. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare Iguras? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the most powerful of the Rare Iguras, Alicia, was still not enough to be our true Eve. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you accomplish by taking away my mom? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have done has been for Altair's future. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of some curse? And what about all the other women you took? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our radar and infrared sensors aren't picking anything up! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one pinging is the graviton sensor! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance of 90! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,60! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,40! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance... 0! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica, Yunoha! Are you all right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, but Yunoha's drained her power... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels hot... what's going on? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this shit?{konchikshoume!} 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening to their bodies? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade, do you read? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy! Are you all right? Where are you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right under you! I'm in the tower! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fine entrance you made. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Amata... with you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's in something called the Alicia Room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be true... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you see the magnitude of the curse of Eve laid on Altair. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, neither could we. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it happened before our very eyes... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Spada's sword! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Machine Angel! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! Get on! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Zessica and Yunoha don't have much time! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata... so that's your name. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one more thing I absolutely have to tell you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please retreat! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Fire! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've called the other Vectors! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, Amata, take the seats! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, Zessica! Fly up and stay there! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw it up, assholes...{beraboume = old-fashioned "idiot"?} 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, you sound... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk later! We've got incoming! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we cannot play the forbidden melody 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without first fighting in a glorious concerto... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys' Union! Go, Aquarion! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Spada! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we can't stay for long. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll break through in as rapid a toccata as we can play!{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toccata} 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon a boys' moon, Moonlight Rhapsody! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Augmentation! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's filled the thruster exhausts! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say filled? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power... but it can't be! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mix! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's that soldier that led us into a trap! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yank my chain like that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... I'm not kidding, Andy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of Eve is... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even those few Iguras lucky enough to survive here on Altair 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,transform into men in body and mind. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform into men? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Altair's doom. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planet can never bear new life. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the curse of Eve! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mix! She's just had her memories altered by the Altairian military! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's Mix, then I... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never make it with a girl... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I found her and didn't even know it... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to crap out, you guys... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing consciousness too... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade, we have to get out of here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't hold on much longer! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if we can break through the roof,  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll remain in danger unless we can escape the planet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MIX! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MIX! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Element power is out of control! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's opening a hole in space! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nano-black hole! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, stop! Please! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can conduct the scale of darkness! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the note where the scales meet, 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the nexus of power to pierce the dimensions... 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, focus your power into my arrow! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Hole Arrow! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate's open! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, the rest is up to you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, Zessica! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name... is Mixy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid, absolutely splendid. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The puzzle was in pieces, and now it's becoming whole. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The slumbering wings awaken... {is he quoting a lyric or something?} 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it means the Wings of the Sun will be reborn. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the used trash Eve was good for something after all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your awakening will come soon, little puzzle piece. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to where everything began, 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the last puzzle will be complete. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ed} 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could go back to where everything began 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rewind it all like it never happened... 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.14,0:24:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much I've lost, so much I'm going to lose. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.43,0:24:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Kiss. 
